snippet.title: Can You Save The World ? - Free Coronavirus Game TRAILER
snippet.description:
PLAY FOR FREE HERE : https://martin-jacob.itch.io/can-you-save-the-world


Can You Save The World ? is a collaborative project between Prof. Richard Wiseman and developer Martin Jacob.It is a family-friendly educational game to help face the Coronavirus pandemic.Players of all ages can become better at social distancing through playing !
